OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Transport department
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologises for Christmas   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fparty during lockdown      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Department for Transport has       
OL,6, apologised after staff held a Christmas
OL,7, gathering during last year's lockdown. 
OL,9,FIn yet another revelation from the     
OL,10,FDaily Mirror, senior civil servants    
OL,11,Fwere said to be "boozing and dancing"  
OL,12,Fin the building on 16 December 2020.   
OL,14,FThe department confirmed the report,   
OL,15,Fsaying it was "inappropriate" and an   
OL,16,F"error of judgment" by staff.          
OL,18,FA spokesman for Transport Secretary    
OL,19,FGrant Shapps said he had "absolutely no
OL,20,Fidea" about the event.                 
